name: MMAI PureWorld Key To The City V1 - old

metadata.description: Key To The City is a utility NFT which gives you VIP access, gaming, and governance to MMAI PureWorld. Plus, it puts you into a random drawing for a second utility NFT where you can win 1 virtual asset from 2 arenas, 750 stores, 500 offices, 750 convention booths, 1500 mystery cars, or 1500 digital billboards. In addition, you will also get $100 in airdropped MMAI coins when MMAI PureChain is released
